1 AN ACT
2 To amend and reenact R.S. 13:5713(C), relative to autopsies of children; to require coroners
3 to perform autopsies on certain children; to provide for the review of immunization
4 records; to provide for reporting; and to provide for related matters.
5 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
6 Section 1. R.S. 13:5713(C) is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
